    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CaveLoop is a short and challenging game. This game is for people who like a challenge, and like to get better and get further in the game. As the player you are stuck in a short loop and each time you restart the loop in a run, then the enemies get randomly more stronger. By enhancing their stats or attacks. You can keep looping the cave until you escape or you can play for a loop count / high score. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game you can upgrade your character, unlock new weapons and hats. Become powerful and skilled enough to escape being imprisoned in the Cave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In general it takes a couple of hours to complete the game and escape. For people who enjoy finding out how far they can get, there is a few more hours of enjoyment.</p>",
